
About
-----

This is just a little SDL sandbox codebase I'm using to mess around.
At the time of this writing, it implements a tic-tac-toe game.

Setup
-----

Linux (Debian-like) prerequisites:

  apt-get install libsdl1.2-dev libsdl-image1.2-dev

OS X (Macports) prerequisites:

  port install libsdl libsd_image

Build
-----

To build on Linux:

  make

To build on OS X:

  make -f Makefile.osx